snippet.textDisplay: Yes, yes I’m a Bucks fan but I have to mention that while Giannis is awesome and a threat to everyone, the reason that he’s better is not only due to him working on threes...but the awesome supporting cast he has helping him out. Giannis gets all the credit, but people easily forget how important the rest of the roster and the bench for that matter is to him. They pass. They stretch the court. The Bucks could’ve gotten another superstar...but the truth is, they got players to compliment his game and his game compliments. Does this recipe of success look a little familiar to the San Antonio Spurs success? It should.
